---
// Componente About para información personal
---

<section id="sobre-mi" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Know my story and passion for development</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <div class="about-card">
          <h3>My Story</h3>
          <p>
            Soy un desarrollador apasionado con más de 1 año de experiencia creando 
            innovative digital solutions. My journey began with curiosity about how web 
            applications work, and since then I have not stopped learning and growing in 
            this fascinating world of development.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="about-card">
          <h3>My Focus</h3>
          <p>
            I believe in development centered on the user, where each line of code 
            has a clear purpose. I specialize in creating intuitive interfaces and 
            exceptional user experiences, combining best practices with modern design 
            and functionality.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="about-card">
          <h3>My Passion</h3>
          <p>
            What motivates me most is solving complex problems and seeing how my 
            solutions positively impact people's lives. Each project is an opportunity to learn something new and overcome technical challenges.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">50+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Projects Completed</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">1+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Years of Experience</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">15+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Technologies Dominated</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Satisfied Clients</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2d3748;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-title::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -10px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 60px;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b6b, #4ecdc4);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #718096;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .about-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .about-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .about-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2d3748;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .about-card p {
    color: #4a5568;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b6b, #4ecdc4);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    color: #718096;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .about-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .about-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .stat-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
